Summers Says Fiscal Contractions Run Risk of ‘Backfiring’

-- B y   A n d r e w   A t k i n s o n
-- 
2011-09-29T07:52:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-29/summers-says-fiscal-contractions-run-risk-of-backfiring-.html
Former U.S. Treasury Secretary
 Lawrence Summers  said countries seeking to rapidly bring down
their deficits risk damaging the economic growth needed to do
so.  “Fiscal contractions are likely to be just that --
contractions -- and they run the risk of backfiring,” he said
in an interview with BBC Radio 4 broadcast today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andrew Atkinson in London at 
